headline: Labcorp Launches Labcorp Whole Health Solutions to Support Holistic Care
summary: Labcorp (NYSE: LH), a global leader of innovative and comprehensive laboratory services, announced today the launch of Labcorp Whole Health Solutions to support the growing needs of functional medicine, integrative medicine and primary care providers in delivering holistic care. The solution launches specialized test panels and a tailored test menu of more than 1,000 scientifically backed biomarkers for cardiometabolic health, hormones, micronutrients, longevity and whole body wellness.

headline: PreciseDx Continues Path to Commercial Launch: Secures Additional Funding and Announces New Leadership
summary: PreciseDx, the leading innovator behind PreciseBreast, a novel breast cancer diagnostic that is powered by OncoIntelligence, their proprietary AI-platform, today announced the successful closing of $11 million in funding and two key leadership hires. This latest round of funding was led by Eventide Asset Management ("Eventide"), Merck Global Health Innovation Fund and Philips Ventures and included Labcorp, Quest Diagnostics, GenHenn Capital Venture, along with other existing investors.
